### Test 1 — List all books (seed data from DB)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books

###

### Test 2a — Search by keyword
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?q=clean

###

### Test 2b — Limit results
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?limit=2

###

### Test 3 — Create a book
POST http://localhost:8000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Refactoring",
    "author": "Martin Fowler",
    "year": 2018
}

###

### Test 4a — Partial update
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "genre": "Software Craftsmanship"
}

###

### Test 4b — Delete a book
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/books/2

###

### Test 5 — Get one book (exists)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/1

###

### Test 5b — Get one book (not found)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/9999

###

### Test 6 — Validation error (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Just a title"
}

###

### Part F — SQL Injection attempt 1 (id with OR injection)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books/1%20OR%201=1

###

### Part F — SQL Injection attempt 2 (quote escape in q param)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/books?q='%20OR%20'1'='1

POST http://localhost:8000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Refactoring",
    "author": "Kesava",
    "year": 2018
}